You are definitely not alone. I wave at every VW bus that I see, although
that is not very often in this area (Va). This person could be new to owning
a VW bus and not realize that owning a bus is such a great thing that you
feel like waving to all other bus owners. 

I have only had my bus for about 2 months and when I first drove down the
rode and had some other bus owners hanging out the window waving at me, it
almost scared me. At the time I was still trying to learn how to drive it
and not get blown off the road. Now I am one of those crazed bus owners that
hangs out the window to greet other bus owners :)

Corbett

